{"data":[{"date":"07:38 22/06","title":"B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Australia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/bang-c-world-cup-2018-co-hoi-nao-de-dt-australia-di-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Peru sau hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc dien bang C World Cup 2018 sau hai tran.\" title=\"C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bang-c-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111ang n\u1eafm \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng sau. &quot;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&quot; ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 trong tay, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Peru d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin y\u00eau c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 theo l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Ricardo Gareca.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, Australia r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang \u1edf th\u1ebf &quot;c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi&quot; so v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Australia?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 Australia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Peru, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p. Hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Australia van con co hoi de gianh ve vao vong loai truc tiep tai bang C World Cup 2018.\" title=\"\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bang-c-world-cup-2018-co-hoi-nao-de-dt-australia-di-tiep.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n* \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng nhau (2).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean (0-2, 1-3,...). Australia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp khi h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Australia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hoa-australia-hlv-hareide-do-tai-do-cau-thu-dan-mach-met-moi-465-189187.html\">H\u00f2a Australia, HLV Hareide \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-australia-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-dan-mach-465-189184.html\">HLV Bert van Marwijk: L\u1ebd ra \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y Australia ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chuot-tui-xuat-hien-tren-khan-dai-465-189183.html\">Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong ng\u00e0y Australia h\u00f2a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-australia-461-189181.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-19h-ngay-216-ve-di-tiep-cho-linh-chi-462-189131.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (19h ng\u00e0y 21/6): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho &ldquo;L\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo;?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"445","checkdouble":"189217"},{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/argentina-lo-sot-vo-voi-phat-bieu-cua-hlv-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Iceland, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng Argentina.</h2><h2>Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Croatia tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-bang-d-world-cup-2018-421-187428.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span> gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng D n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Iceland s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p Nigeria v\u00e0 Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Argentina-lo-sot-vo-voi-phat-bieu-cua-HLV-Dalic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV&nbsp;Dalic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Argentina r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland t\u1ea1i Rostov. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u00f2n b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, HLV Dalic cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c fan trung l\u1eadp. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, theo d\u00f5i Croatia ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Croatia chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod trong khi Argentina quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp bu\u1ed5i cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Moscow tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u1edf s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Croatia th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong 2 ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec Argentina qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 m\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi C\u0110V \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Croatia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/sampaoli-bao-chua-cho-su-mat-tich-cua-messi-469-189213.html\">Sampaoli nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-tham-croatia-argentina-phai-lam-gi-de-vuot-qua-vong-bang-421-189208.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Croatia, Argentina ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"444","checkdouble":"189218"},{"date":"07:36 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-quang-nam-vs-hai-phong-17h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland ho\u1eb7c Nigeria m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 Iceland \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c \u1edf Euro 2016 khi x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Hungary nh\u01b0ng thua v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Iceland ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNha s\u1ef9 ki\u00eam HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Iceland ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat 19 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ghi th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIceland sau b\u00e0n thua v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alfred Finnbogason. Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson khi\u1ebfn Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Iceland c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Argentina, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Gylfi Sigurdsson hay Alfreo Finnbogason ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n Iceland th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria vs Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng Argentina, Iceland ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfn xa gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia-421-189189.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Argentina vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Iceland l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeri \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Victor Moses, Alex Iwobi, Kelechi Iheanacho hay John Obi Mikel.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-(22h00-ngay-226)-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ngang ng\u1eeda so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Salisu Yusuf c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, song l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft d\u00ednh. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nigeria ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Croatia l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Francis Uzoho 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u00edt so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThua 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi Iceland. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Nigeria c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n Nigeria c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Iceland \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Nigeria ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0. 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iceland vs Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-1-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 1-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"443","checkdouble":"189219"},{"date":"07:42 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-quang-ninh-vs-khanh-hoa-18h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/than-quang-ninh-vs-sanna-khanh-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14, danh s\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u01a1ng binh c\u1ee7a Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Vinicius \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u01a1, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Thanh Hi\u1ec1n, V\u0103n Khoa, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Nguy\u00ean Sa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eeda h\u1eadn \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. V\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 do CLB\u00a0t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean nhau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u201cngang t\u00e0ng\u201d. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1 trong 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh: Tu\u1ea5n Linh, Tu\u1ea5n T\u00fa, M\u1ea1c Qu\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Huy, Vi\u1ebft Tri\u1ec1u, Nh\u1eadt Minh, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Huy C\u01b0\u1eddng, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, Edyson.<br>\r\nKh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, Nh\u1eadt Nam, Zarour, Duy Thanh, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, Toure, Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed, Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh, Ho\u00e0i An, Tr\u1ecdng B\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"442","checkdouble":"189220"},{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-226-khong-con-duong-lui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: G\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e0ng \u0111i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf kh\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1p cu\u1ed1i TP.HCM, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua g\u1ed3m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/HAGL-Saigon.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u1ea7n&nbsp; gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL \u00edt khi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi. B\u1edfi khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, NHM c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi HAGL, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-2 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00fac n\u00e0y tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sai Gon vs HAGL\" title=\"S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi HAGL. 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n th\u1eafng 2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 sau 90 ph\u00fat so t\u00e0i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7&nbsp;Vincent Bossou. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i binh, HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2, d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec trong tay \u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e1ng lo nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 V-League. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 22/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 15 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Lich-thi-dau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018: HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\">Thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HAGL s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi?</span><br />\r\nSau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"441","checkdouble":"189221"},{"date":"07:54 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/iceland-vs-nigeria-22h00-ngay-226-chien-binh-hay-dai-bang.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland ho\u1eb7c Nigeria m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 Iceland \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c \u1edf Euro 2016 khi x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Hungary nh\u01b0ng thua v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Iceland ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNha s\u1ef9 ki\u00eam HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Iceland ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat 19 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ghi th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIceland sau b\u00e0n thua v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alfred Finnbogason. Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson khi\u1ebfn Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Iceland c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Argentina, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Gylfi Sigurdsson hay Alfreo Finnbogason ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n Iceland th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria vs Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng Argentina, Iceland ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfn xa gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia-421-189189.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Argentina vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Iceland l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeri \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Victor Moses, Alex Iwobi, Kelechi Iheanacho hay John Obi Mikel.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-(22h00-ngay-226)-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ngang ng\u1eeda so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Salisu Yusuf c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, song l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft d\u00ednh. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nigeria ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Croatia l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Francis Uzoho 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u00edt so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThua 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi Iceland. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Nigeria c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n Nigeria c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Iceland \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Nigeria ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0. 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iceland vs Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-1-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 1-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"440","checkdouble":"189222"},{"date":"08:38 22/06","title":"HLV Brazil x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-brazil-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-neymar-o-tran-gap-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Costa Rica, HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar.</h2><h2>Neymar \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Costa Rica</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar\" title=\"Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/hlv-brazil-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-neymar-o-tran-gap-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Neymar \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Costa Rica</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica th\u00ec&nbsp; Neymar \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u00ec to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 World Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c HLV \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Brazil ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 hi sinh. Ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa hi\u1ec7p gi\u1eefa gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 trung th\u1ef1c&rdquo;, HLV Tite n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Thiago Silva n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111ang kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Brazil. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cao h\u01a1n ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Costa Rica t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil khi gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 Uruguay, Anh v\u00e0 Italia. V\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Brazil. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nThiago Silva c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Brazil l\u00e0 ai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i Brazil v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Costa \u0111\u00e3 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Brazil vs Costa Rica s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"439","checkdouble":"189223"},{"date":"08:56 22/06","title":"John Stones: \"Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-ronaldo-va-cu-nhay-tren-dinh-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>John Stones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stones kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/anh-vs-tunisia-bang-g-463-188846.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Tunisia</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 song Tam s\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"John Stones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"John Stones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-ronaldo-va-cu-nhay-tren-dinh-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>John Stones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJohn Stones ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. World Cup l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, song quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Tam s\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i, song Stones l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, song Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>John Stones h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed John Stones, Kyle Walker v\u00e0 Harry Maguire l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola phat bieu ve John Stones\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 John Stones\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/man-city-phu-nhan-co-the-ban-bom-tan-47-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>John Stones h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng Walker v\u00e0 Maguire \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean li\u00ean l\u1ea1c trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"438","checkdouble":"189227"},{"date":"08:46 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica (19h ng\u00e0y 22/6): \u0110\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Selecao\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-costa-rica-19h-ngay-226-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-selecao.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac \u0110T Brazil bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00f3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, \u0110T Brazil l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1 d\u00f9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n cho vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Selecao. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 20 nh\u1edd c\u00fa s\u00fat xa tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPaulinho kh\u00f4ng t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Willian c\u0169ng x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1i t\u0103m, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Neymar b\u1ecb ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u00e1t sao, s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Brazil ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3 v\u00e0o Coutinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h ng\u00e0y 226 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h ng\u00e0y 226 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Nhan-dinh-Brazil-vs-Costa-Rica-19h-ngay-226-bang-B-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar b\u1ecb ch\u0103m s\u00f3c chu \u0111\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, t\u1edbi khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a r\u1ed3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1, Brazil v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. H\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, \u0110T Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef v\u1ec1 Neymar. Trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong su\u1ed1t 3 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-brazil-nhan-tin-du-ve-neymar-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si-421-188899.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/dt-brazil-nhan-tin-du-ve-neymar-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-brazil-nhan-tin-du-ve-neymar-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si-421-188899.html\">\u0110T Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef v\u1ec1 Neymar sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica, \u0110T Brazil \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar sau nh\u1eefng va ch\u1ea1m \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a r\u00f5 Neymar c\u00f3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 5 n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. H\u1ecd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ri\u00eang Valon Behrami b\u00e1m theo Neymar v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Neymar c\u00f3 k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, anh n\u00ean chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u00f3 b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 theo s\u00e1t &ldquo;ti\u1ec3u Pele&rdquo; nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh c\u0169ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brazil vs Costa Rica\" title=\"Preview Brazil vs Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2262018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h ng\u00e0y 22/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nSelecao ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n bung s\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 20, Brazil l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y HLV Tite ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap cho Brazil c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tan v\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o Brazil c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Cho t\u1edbi khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean, Selecao c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. H\u1eb3n HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u1eadt d\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite tinh toan sai lam\" title=\"HLV Tite tinh toan sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/HLV-Tite-tinh-toan-sai-lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y Tite l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn xa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Brazil c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng gi\u1eef g\u00ecn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t r\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Costa Rica s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Brazil s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Brazil s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1eadt s\u1edbm tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00ean b\u00f3ng y nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Costa Rica phong ngu so dong\" title=\"Costa Rica phong ngu so dong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Costa-Rica-phong-ngu-so-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Costa Rica s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCosta Rica kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thua 1 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alex Kolarov.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o, Costa Rica h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i lo nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Brazil c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Selecao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nBrazil (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Alisson - 14.Danilo, 2.Silva, 3.Miranda, 12.Marcelo - 15.Paulinho, 5.Casemiro, 11.Coutinho - 19.Willian, 9.Jesus, 10.Neymar.<br>\r\n<strong>Costa Rica (3-4-2-1):</strong> 1.Navas - 2.Acosta, 3.Gonz\u00e1lez, 6.Duarte - 16.Gamboa, 5.Borges, 20.Guzm\u00e1n, 15.Calvo - 7.Bolanos, 10.Ruiz - 21.Urena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Brazil vs Costa Rica\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Brazil-vs-Costa-Rica-(4-3-3-vs-3-4-2-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/wenger-chi-ra-2-van-de-cua-brazil-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si-469-188796.html\">Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Brazil sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neymar-chi-trich-trong-tai-sau-khi-brazil-bi-cam-hoa-469-188790.html\">Neymar ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi Brazil b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-ban-thua-oan-va-mat-11m-marcelo-noi-gi-421-188788.html\">Nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua oan v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t 11m, Marcelo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-thuy-sy-danh-gia-cao-1-diem-co-duoc-truoc-brazil-421-188787.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"437","checkdouble":"189231"},{"date":"08:51 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 23/6): \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d l\u1ea1i bay cao?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-serbia-vs-thuy-si-1h-ngay-236-dai-bang-lai-bay-cao.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Serbia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Serbia th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica d\u00f9 s\u00e1t n\u00fat nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 Serbia. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Serbia l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. D\u00f9 d\u00e2ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean cao hay ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Ivanovic, Tosic, Kolarov v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Milenkovic. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Milivojevic v\u00e0 Matic c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t c\u1ef1c hay, r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u1ea5y Costa Rica c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 236) \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i bay ca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 236) \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i bay ca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Nhan-dinh-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Si-(1h-ngay-236)-Dai-bang-lai-bay-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a HLV Mladen Krstajic l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb g\u00f2 b\u00f3 trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Lazio ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau Mitrovic. Anh t\u1ea1o 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n cho trung phong c\u1ee7a Serbia v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, Milinkovic-Savic c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa &ldquo;n\u00e3 ph\u00e1o&rdquo; t\u1ea7m xa uy l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 20 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia danh bai Costa Rica 1-0\" title=\"Serbia danh bai Costa Rica 1-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Serbia-danh-bai-Costa-Rica-1-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u00e0 c\u1ea3 kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Serbia b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n hay c\u1ee7a Matic, Ljajic, Tadic; nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic, Milenkovic, Mitrovic; nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic, Tadic, Kolarov.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. Ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kolarov \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Serbia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Costa Rica. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed n\u1ebfu c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u1ebf c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cham-diem-costa-rica-01-serbia-nguoi-hung-kolarov-421-188746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/cham-diem-costa-rica-01-serbia-nguoi-hung-kolarov.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cham-diem-costa-rica-01-serbia-nguoi-hung-kolarov-421-188746.html\">Ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m Costa Rica 0-1 Serbia: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Kolarov</span><br>\r\n<span>G\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Alex Kolarov, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea5m...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Brazil, song \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zuber th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 song t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng. H\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Preview Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1h ng\u00e0y 23/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Serbia. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng ngay 90 ph\u00fat s\u1eafp t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kaliningrad. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Serbia \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh &ldquo;\u0111\u00eam d\u00e0i l\u1eafm m\u1ed9ng&rdquo;, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Serbia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Brazil. M\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, Serbia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i Brazil. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSerbia (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Stojkovic - 6.Ivanovic, 15.Milenkovic, 3.Tosic, 56.Kolarov - 21.Matic, 4.Milivojevic - 22.Ljajic, 20.Milinkovic-Savic, 10.Tadic - 9.Mitrovic.<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Sommer - 2.Lichtsteiner, 22.Schar, 5.Akanji, 13.Rodriguez - 10.Xhaka, 11.Behrami - 23.Shaqiri, 15.Dzemaili, 14.Zuber - 9.Seferovic.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Serbia 1-0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"436","checkdouble":"189232"},{"date":"04:09 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.\r\n</h2><h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273029/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Caballero<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Iceland, nh\u01b0ng Willy Caballero v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Sampaoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 sang 3 trung v\u1ec7, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Caballero, trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui l\u00f2ng, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi anh c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 c\u0103m ph\u1eabn. Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Caballero ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho&hellip; Rebic ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i &ldquo;s\u1edf th\u00edch&rdquo; chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 World Cup, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea1m nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Caballero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Caballero tiep tuc lam tro he trong khung go\" title=\"Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/willy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 nhanh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi th\u1ebf th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iceland, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m nay thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh tr\u1ed1ng (Perez b\u1ecf l\u1ee1), v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7, Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, m\u00e0&hellip; bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, khi\u1ebfn Caballero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu Rakitic c\u1ee7a Croatia d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thua 0-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina\" title=\"Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/argen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Sampaoli \u0111ang ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 ng\u00e0y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3: Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh HLV n\u00e0y th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn&hellip; kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, \u00f4ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi xoay sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 y\u1ebfu nay c\u00f2n y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n, trong khi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Sampaoli \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 Dybala l\u1eabn Higuain v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u00f2 tr\u1ed1ng g\u00ec. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111ang m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sampaoli\" title=\"Sampaoli\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/sam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia: S\u1ef1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Sampaoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Croatia<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh c\u1ee7a Dalic, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca-ro ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ed1i nguy n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Ivan Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3, khi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang. Luka Modric khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u1ee9c l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, trong khi Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Leo Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1n t\u1eed, khi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u mong Iceland kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, m\u1edbi c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Argentina 0-3 Croatia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 0-3 Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thong-so-Argentina.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 0-3 Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai cua bang D World Cup 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/tram.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\">Argentina 0-3 Croatia (KT): Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Albiceleste thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n k\u00e9m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina-465-189201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina-465-189201.html\">Luka Modric: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng cho anh ta nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng</span><br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng cho Lionel Messi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"435","checkdouble":"189200"},{"date":"04:03 22/06","title":"Luka Modric: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng cho anh ta nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng cho Lionel Messi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Croatia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Willy Caballero gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat xa hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Argentina, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Rakitic ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina: &quot;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y nh\u00ecn th\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00fang, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. Ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 3-0 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Sau hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Davor Suker t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, Modric c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: &quot;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn, ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Croatia t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng Croatia kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ed9i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Iceland v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\">Argentina 0-3 Croatia (KT): Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Albiceleste thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n k\u00e9m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"434","checkdouble":"189201"},{"date":"04:25 22/06","title":"Jorge Sampaoli: \"Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nArgentina tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho thi\u00ean h\u1ea1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng d\u00f9 Albiceleste ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ebfm ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rebic, Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Argentina trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@GaryLineker: </strong></em>&ldquo;M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Croatia, nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1eebng \u1ea5y n\u0103m theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/me.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi v\u00e0 Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><strong><br>\r\n@Jermainejunior:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau Copa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@WelBeast:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho Sampaoli v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean anh ta \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland. N\u1ebfu qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@katienolan:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho Salah c\u1ee7a Argentina.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@MiguelDelaney: </strong></em>&ldquo;Messi r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Khi b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y quay l\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Messi v\u00e0 Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/meca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><em>@YahooSportUK:</em></strong> &ldquo;C\u00f3 ai th\u1ea5y Messi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ecm tr\u1ebb l\u1ea1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>@RodolfoLanderos: </em></strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9? Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat c\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\">Jorge Sampaoli: Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nThua th\u1ea3m Croatia, HLV Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Leo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"433","checkdouble":"189202"},{"date":"04:30 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina trong tr\u1eadn thua Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Messi-can-lam-gi-de-ngan-Argentina-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.\r\n</h2><h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua C\u1ed9ng h\u00f2a S\u00e9c 1-6 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1958.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1edf h\u1eefu 11 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y Messi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ghi 1 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup (n\u0103m 2002).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3\" title=\"Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhung-thong-ke-tham-hai-cua-argentina-trong-tran-thua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 &ndash; T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 pha ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Gonzalo Higuain (1) v\u00e0 Sergio Aguero (1) trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup, sau Davor Suker v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 &ndash; Croatia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9, t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 &ndash; Caballero l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 4 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, sau David De Gea, Wojciech Szczesny v\u00e0 Mohammed Al-Owais.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/willy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n4 &ndash; Luka Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, sau Cris Ronaldo, Coutinho v\u00e0 Nacho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">100 &ndash; T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % c\u1ee7a Luka Modric trong c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi (2/2), t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng (2/2) v\u00e0 th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn (3/3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\">Jorge Sampaoli: Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nThua th\u1ea3m Croatia, HLV Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Leo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"432","checkdouble":"189203"},{"date":"04:52 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Argentina thua th\u1ea3m Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p khi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia \u0111\u00e2m cho ba nh\u00e1t ki\u1ebfm t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Argentina thua th\u1ea3m Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Argentina thua th\u1ea3m Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/043608-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Diego Maradona.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac CDV Argentina khong co ve vao san phai tap trung theo doi tran dau o khu Fan Zone.\" title=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V Argentina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf khu Fan Zone.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/043703-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c C\u0110V Argentina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf khu Fan Zone.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td st